Stay the hell out of my business.

317
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,160
Tawan.

318
00:27:12,320 --> 00:27:13,560
Tawan.

319
00:27:22,520 --> 00:27:23,560
Tawan.

320
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:27,520
Hindi ka na babalik dahil sa batang iyon?

321
