Mamimiss ko ang luto mo
so much kapag nandoon ako.

385
00:34:23,200 --> 00:34:24,960
Pagkain lang ang kulang?

386
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:27,280
Paano ang "tao?"

387
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:29,000
Maanghang din siya.

388
00:34:29,920 --> 00:34:31,200
Looksoh.

389
00:34:32,720 --> 00:34:33,919
Sailom,

390
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:35,639
Bilisan mo at ga-graduate ka na.

391
00:34:35,640 --> 00:34:37,760
Maawa ka sa lalaking ito dito.

392
