Mamimiss talaga kita ng sobra.

401
00:35:47,120 --> 00:35:50,280
Huwag masyadong madrama.
Mag-aaral siya, hindi sa digmaan.

402
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:52,040
Tama ba, Sailom?

403
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:54,680
Sailom?

404
00:35:57,240 --> 00:35:58,800
