naghihintay nang walang anumang layunin.

433
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:12,160
Ngunit sa iyo,

434
00:38:12,720 --> 00:38:15,680
Sigurado akong hindi magiging ganoon.

435
00:38:17,720 --> 00:38:20,200
Nakikita kitang nagmamadali dito ngayon

436
00:38:22,600 --> 00:38:25,080
