473
00:43:04,320 --> 00:43:05,840
Naiintindihan mo, Nanay.

474
00:43:14,240 --> 00:43:15,480
Nanay,

475
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:18,199
nakatitig siya sa phone niya

476
00:43:18,200 --> 00:43:20,400
at pagmo-mope ng ganito sa loob ng isang linggo ngayon.

477
00:43:20,720 --> 00:43:23,400
Ganyan talaga siya
nang makipaghiwalay siya kay P'Yanin.

478
00:43:23,440 --> 00:43:24,920
Hindi sa tingin ko, sweetie.

479
00:43:27,800 --> 00:43:30,960
Nabnueng, handa na ang kape mo.

480
00:43:53,840 --> 00:43:55,400
Eto, tutulungan kita.

481
00:43:55,440 --> 00:43:56,640
Salamat.

482
00:44:14,200 --> 00:44:15,480
P'Dindin.

483
00:44:16,400 --> 00:44:17,720
Hoy, Looksoh.

484
00:44:18,960 --> 00:44:21,600
Ilang linggo lang akong wala.

485
00:44:21,800 --> 00:44:23,440
Paano naging masikip dito?

486
00:44:23,480 --> 00:44:26,439
P'Nava kasi eh
nagsimula ng TikTok channel

487
00:44:26,440 --> 00:44:29,520
at naglalabasan na siya
P'Mickey at P'Zoom na nilalaman.

488
00:44:31,080 --> 00:44:32,840
Wow, ang galing.

489
00:44:32,880 --> 00:44:37,680
Pero sa dami ng customer,
kaya ba ni Sky ang lahat ng ito mag-isa?

490
00:44:37,720 --> 00:44:40,760
Oh, hindi ginagawa ni P'Sky
ang pag-aayos pa.

491
00:44:40,960 --> 00:44:46,160
Nag-hire siya ng mechanics
at sa halip ay naging part dealer.

492
00:44:47,880 --> 00:44:53,880
Nagbebenta daw siya ng parts
ay mas kumikita kaysa sa pag-aayos sa kanila.

493
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:57,280
Kapag hindi siya nakikipagkita sa mga kliyente,

494
00:44:57,320 --> 00:44:59,960
baka tinutulungan niya si P'Nava sa wedding shoots.

495
00:45:00,080 --> 00:45:03,120
At... paano ang Tawan?

496
00:45:03,200 --> 00:45:04,640
Anong ginagawa niya ngayon?

497
00:45:04,680 --> 00:45:06,280
P'Tawan's...

498
00:45:06,320 --> 00:45:07,600
Dindin.

499
00:45:38,000 --> 00:45:39,960
Ngayon, bigyan ang isa't isa ng kaunting halik.

500
00:45:41,760 --> 00:45:42,800
Okay.

501
00:45:42,840 --> 00:45:44,040
Ayos ba ang ilaw?

502
00:45:46,320 --> 00:45:47,720
Maganda.

503
00:45:48,280 --> 00:45:50,320
Napapagod?

504
00:45:50,480 --> 00:45:51,879
Hindi naman, babe.

505
00:45:51,880 --> 00:45:52,960
Bigyan mo ako ng halik?

506
00:45:54,840 --> 00:45:56,960
Tinanggap ko kayo para magtrabaho!

507
00:45:57,000 --> 00:45:59,440
Paano ka magiging
mas sweet pa sa grooms?!

508
00:45:59,480 --> 00:46:01,720
Bumalik ka sa shooting!

509
00:46:05,160 --> 00:46:06,360
Nandito pa rin?!

510
00:46:06,400 --> 00:46:07,840
Sige, sige.

511
00:46:09,720 --> 00:46:11,760
- Kumusta ang sumasalamin?
- Sapat na.

512
00:46:12,600 --> 00:46:14,440
Magkano pa
maglalakad ka?!

513
00:46:14,640 --> 00:46:15,960
Dindin!

514
00:46:22,040 --> 00:46:23,640
Saan ka napunta?

515
00:46:23,680 --> 00:46:26,440
Tumawag ako, nagtext, hindi ka nagrereply.

516
00:46:26,880 --> 00:46:28,239
Ano ang mali sa iyo?

517
00:46:28,240 --> 00:46:30,560
Bumalik ako sa pagiging piloto,
tulad ng gusto mo.

518
00:46:30,600 --> 00:46:33,760
Lumilipad ka ba sa outer space?
Bakit hindi ka nagreply?

519
00:46:34,320 --> 00:46:35,760
pasensya na po.

520
00:46:36,760 --> 00:46:39,080
Gusto ko lang ipagmalaki mo ako,

521
00:46:40,040 --> 00:46:42,080
kasing proud ako sayo.

522
00:46:44,040 --> 00:46:46,200
Pinaghirapan kong maging piloto muli

523
00:46:47,440 --> 00:46:49,280
para lang hilingin na maging boyfriend kita.

524
00:46:50,200 --> 00:46:51,400
Maghintay...

525
00:46:53,800 --> 00:46:55,560
ano ang sinabi mo?

526
00:46:55,600 --> 00:46:56,920
Bingi ka ba?

527
00:46:59,840 --> 00:47:01,200
Ano ang magiging?

528
00:47:01,560 --> 00:47:03,120
Magiging boyfriend kita?

529
00:47:06,720 --> 00:47:07,920
ayos lang.

530
00:47:08,400 --> 00:47:09,640
I guess gagawin ko.

531
00:47:13,280 --> 00:47:15,480
You look pretty hot in that uniform.

532
00:47:20,840 --> 00:47:23,560
Maghanap tayo ng kung saan... para alisin ito.

533
00:47:26,280 --> 00:47:28,520
kanina ko pa gustong
maghubad ng damit ng piloto sa mahabang panahon.

534
00:47:29,040 --> 00:47:30,719
Sabihin mo lang malibog ka.

535
00:47:30,720 --> 00:47:32,240
At ikaw ay hindi?

536
00:47:48,920 --> 00:47:50,200
P'Doc,

537
00:47:50,400 --> 00:47:52,000
samahan mo akong lumangoy!

538
00:47:52,200 --> 00:47:54,440
Huwag mo akong hayaang mag-isa!

539
00:47:55,160 --> 00:47:56,560
P'Doc!

540
00:47:59,680 --> 00:48:02,320
Sabi mo maghintay ako...

541
00:48:05,680 --> 00:48:07,760
at nandito pa rin ako, naghihintay sayo.

542
00:48:49,320 --> 00:48:50,840
P'Doc Nabnueng!

543
00:49:00,680 --> 00:49:03,680
Alam kong makikita kita dito!

544
00:49:29,800 --> 00:49:32,000
Bakit hindi mo sinasagot ang mga tawag ko?

545
00:49:33,080 --> 00:49:35,120
Hindi mo rin sinagot ang akin.

546
00:49:39,080 --> 00:49:42,800
Ito ay dahil sa mga time zone,
kaya hindi nagtugma ang aming mga iskedyul.

547
00:49:44,680 --> 00:49:46,120
Sandali lang.

548
00:49:46,760 --> 00:49:48,880
Ginagawa mo ba ito...

549
00:49:49,760 --> 00:49:51,560
para balikan ako?

550
00:49:55,880 --> 00:49:58,200
Ito ay dapat na maging isang sorpresa.

551
00:50:01,400 --> 00:50:05,240
Nagpasya akong mag-drop out sa U.S.
unibersidad

552
00:50:06,360 --> 00:50:08,639
at ilipat pabalik sa
isang Thai.

553
00:50:08,640 --> 00:50:11,080
Sa wakas ay magkakasabay na ang ating oras.

554
00:50:11,800 --> 00:50:13,200
Ngayon,

555
00:50:14,080 --> 00:50:17,280
kailangan mong sagutin ang mga video call ko.

556
00:50:17,560 --> 00:50:19,480
Wala nang dahilan.

557
00:50:21,760 --> 00:50:23,200
gagawin ko.

558
00:50:24,520 --> 00:50:27,280
I-video call kita...

559
00:50:28,480 --> 00:50:30,200
hanggang sa pagtanda natin.

560
00:50:30,560 --> 00:50:31,600
kamusta kana?

561
00:50:33,280 --> 00:50:35,200
Ito ba ay isang panukala?

562
00:50:36,320 --> 00:50:37,640
Gusto mo ba?

563
00:50:38,360 --> 00:50:39,360
Halika.

564
00:50:39,361 --> 00:50:42,280
Irehistro na natin ang kasal natin.

565
00:50:43,240 --> 00:50:45,480
Aba... huminahon ka, P'Doc.

566
00:50:45,920 --> 00:50:47,880
Estudyante pa ako.

567
00:50:51,320 --> 00:50:52,880
namiss kita ng sobra.

568
00:51:46,080 --> 00:51:47,400
P'Doc.

569
00:51:48,600 --> 00:51:49,880
Oo?

570
00:51:50,720 --> 00:51:55,000
Naaalala mo ba ang unang pagkakataon
niyaya mo akong magbisikleta?

571
00:51:57,960 --> 00:51:59,880
Syempre ginagawa ko. Bakit?

572
00:52:01,800 --> 00:52:05,560
Actually, hindi ako mahilig mag-cycling noon.

573
00:52:06,600 --> 00:52:08,480
Napunta lang ako

574
00:52:09,520 --> 00:52:11,120
dahil sayo.

575
00:52:12,760 --> 00:52:14,119
alam ko na yan.

576
00:52:14,120 --> 00:52:15,240
ha?

577
00:52:17,520 --> 00:52:20,120
Iyong mga mata ang nagbigay nito.

578
00:52:21,000 --> 00:52:22,400
Aminin mo.

579
00:52:29,040 --> 00:52:30,360
Paano naman ngayon?

580
00:52:31,120 --> 00:52:33,400
Mas gusto mo ba ang pagbibisikleta?

581
00:52:39,880 --> 00:52:41,600
Mahal ko ito higit sa anupaman.

582
00:52:48,920 --> 00:52:50,480
Pero sa totoo lang,

583
00:52:51,600 --> 00:52:53,720
Gagawin ko ang lahat

584
00:52:54,680 --> 00:52:56,640
basta kasama kita.

585
00:52:57,760 --> 00:53:01,200
Iyon lang ang kailangan ko.

